      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "nation-wide networks, - she has faced the officials",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "on Capitol Hill. She has met the Brothers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "FRED STECKLING has taken a unique movie-film",
