    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "which has impressed NASA's photographic experts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "and the men at the Pentagon. He has met the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "Brothers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Can it be CO-INCIDENCE all the time? Can they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "FAKE unique and impressive evidence ALL THE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
